race.comment: BETWITCHERY (10) is a progressive visitor who scored last time at Pakenham when well fancied. Trip suits and now found form can give a sight again. VEXATIOUS DANCER (1) has been close to a win and is having first try this trip. This is easier than last start and deserves to break through. TAPINFORPAR (9) was a fresh-up winner then not far away this trip last time. Is a third-up winner and rates a leading player. STREETCAR APOLLO (3) is also racing well. Runner-up fresh then was a strong winner last time. Harder here but hard to knock. ZEBELLA (4) has been thereabouts for seemingly an eternity. Goes well here and off the low draw will give a sight.
